# OpenClaw Workspace Backup

Auto-generated backup of agent configuration and memory.

## Included

- **Configs/** - Agent identity, SOUL, AGENTS.md, etc.
- **Daily/** - Daily notes and logs
- **memory/** - Session memory and heartbeat state
- **workflows/** - Scripts and workflows (YouTube transcript, etc.)
- **Emergency-Backup/** - Recovery information

## Excluded

- **.openclaw/** - Runtime session files (transcripts, temp data)

